fields.body: not only for raising money for my precious son’s charity fund raiser at the Park Gate Inn, Cannock Wood, but also for bombarding those who attended with many ‘spot on’ messages. She certainly gave the sceptics something to think about. Trinity’s easy manner, confidence and complete trust in the spirit world resulted in many desperately needed poignant messages coming through.
fields.title: Grateful thanks to Trinity

fields.body: I and other members of my family had the pleasure of meeting Trinity recently. I speak for us all when I say that we all found our experiences truly uplifting and comforting. Trinity gave lots of spot-on accurate information, and the messages of love we received from our loved ones who have passed was wonderful. I cannot praise Trinity enough for her fantastic work!
fields.title: Uplifting and comforting

fields.body: I have met Trinity on a number of occasions and had 3 readings including a telephone reading. I have been greatly comforted by the messages she has given me from my Mum. The information she passes on is so accurate. I would recommend Trinity to anyone, she is a warm kind and honest lady and I thank her for bringing peace of mind to me. Thank you Trinity
fields.title: Bringing peace of mind

fields.body: We would both like to send our thanks for the help you gave us. We have taken so much comfort from the reading which makes so much sense to us in our times of trouble. We hope you will see us again and we will certainly value and welcome any advice or guidance you are kind enough to offer! Take care and thank you once again
fields.title: Thank you for the help

fields.body: I visited Trinity at her home for a private reading in March; I had seen her in Oswestry in one of her shows and found the whole experience fascinating. As soon as she opened the door to me with her welcoming smile I felt completely at ease. Her accuracy and knowledge of my dear Mother was both comforting and truly unbelievable. Trinity, thank you once again for your hospitality, especially the cup of tea my Mum told you to offer me. Sue
fields.title: Thank you

fields.body:
Trinity you came to my parent’s home on the 19th march Monday night, I was very excited I had been waiting for the evening for a long time, the reading was for me and my mom, she is a Christian but is not in touch with her faith, I am in a deep relationship with the lord so knew what to expect. However when entering the house I felt warm and loved immediately, a great big smile on her face and dancing around I was weary of her movements however found out she had 2 much coffee during the day and needed to use the w.c, lol sorry Trinity. We sat together very chilled out, and immediately she started pacing up and down the living room, my grandmother came thru immediately, my mom was weary however we had a whole hour of continuous clarification that my nan had come thru to apologise 2 my mom and explain why she was so cold with my mom. Information I didn’t even know and certainly no one else could no, aww I did not want it to end, she was spot on exact and true to every word she said we felt her love.
EVERYONE READING THESE TESTIMONIALS PLEASE NOTE I RECOMMEND TRINITY HIGHLY SHE IS WONDERFUL AND VERY FLEXIBLE ON MEETINGS! LOVE U SO MUCH GOD BLESS U TRINITY YOU’RE DOING YOUR GRANDFATHER PROUD TRULY A BLESSING FROM HEAVEN CHICK GOD BLESS AMY XX
fields.title: I recommend Trinity highly

fields.body: I live in Spain and did a telephone reading with Trinity on February 21st. I had never done a reading before and was dubious about how a telephone reading would work. Well, let me say that distance does not in any way affect Trinity’s gift. I have no doubt that Trinity is incredibly gifted; the detail she went into was astounding and absolutely spot on! For anyone thinking about a telephone reading, I can’t recommend Trinity highly enough, you will not be disappointed! Trinity, thank you sincerely for confirming that there IS an afterlife. It meant so much to me to have had that contact with my beloved Grandmother and Father and knowing they are OK and watching over me. I feel so grateful that there are people like you whose mission it is to help others deal with bereavement. You have made my loss a lot easier to bear. I will definitely be using your services again in the future and plan to visit a Spiritualist Church next time I am in England! Love
fields.title: Telephone reading with Trinity

fields.body: I would just like to say what a brilliant night I had last night at Goodyear Pavilion. I didn't get a message myself but my sister did and it was nice to know that our mother was with us and that she loves us loads. When you are under the weather and feeling a bit low this is just the pick me up you need never mind the gin and tonics this is worth more. I have been to see several mediums in my time and I can honestly say hand on heart Trinity is the best. I would put her on a par with my mom THE BEST. I will be making regular visits to Trinity from now on. Keep up the good work
fields.title: Brilliant nigh at Goodyear Pavilion

fields.body: I want to say a huge thank you to Trinity for confirming to me there is an afterlife! I lost my Mom in December and I visited Trinity hoping she would come through – and she did. Before my Mom died we had agreed a code word to use to prove to me if there was an afterlife, and it was the first thing Trinity mentioned to me! I was stunned. Everything she told me was accurate and has given me so much comfort to know my Mom is still with me. She even told me that my Mom knew I had bought some boots the day before! Trinity is the loveliest lady & instantly put me at ease. I have already recommended her to family & friends and will be seeing her again soon Lots of love xxx
fields.title: Confirmed there is an afterlife, I was stunned

fields.body: A couple of weeks ago I had a phone reading with Trinity  A lot of people I know assumed you had to have a face to face reading to connect to the spirit world, how wrong they were. It was brilliant in every aspect. My beloved mum came through and I am still smiling. I can smile at the cupboard that sticks every time I open it. Trinity picked up on this, and many more things which were detailed. I jotted 4 pages down not easy to do whilst listening to Trinity; I can’t stop reading it. The spirit world is there and Trinity was my telephonist to them. Trinity created a warm and glowing presence which I held in my heart.
fields.title: God Bless you Trinity

fields.body: I met Trinity by chance at London Bridge Station in 2006 and we were trying to find the right platform for a train, it turned out we were both about to find the same one. We got on well and chatted on the train and suddenly she told me to tell her no more about me and gave me the most incredible message from my Dad!!! She was spot on, the words were absolutely from him, no doubt about that (I was even told to sit up straight! – Dad’s words, always! – and my home was described in great detail, plus so much more!!!) This was such a wonderful meeting and we both ended up in "happy" tears. Meeting Trinity was amazing and to this day I cherish it. I must add that Trinity is such a lovely lady and I feel bad for not having written this years ago. She is truly amazing in every sense and anyone who knows her will understand that spiritually and as a friend Trinity is incredibly special. Thanks my friend who came out of nowhere, you are an amazing and special lady with a marvellous gift. Love Mxxx
fields.title: Dad’s words

fields.body: I went to see Trinity in Dec 09, whilst I was suffering the lowest point in my life. My friend recommended Trinity, so I went with an open mind. It was literally a life changing experience; with direct messages from my Grandmother. I was told that the next year my life would change…and it changed dramatically! Two years on, I have come across your website and I just wanted to say thank you for passing on such valuable messages and giving me the hope that I so needed x
fields.title: Thank you

fields.body: I would like to thank Trinity for her amazing work she did at Pelsall social club Thursday 10th Nov 2011 it was so enjoyable and warm how Trinity brought love ones back to so many people that evening we are hoping to have Trinity back next yr. I would recommend this lady to anyone
fields.title: I recommend Trinity

fields.body: I had a reading today with Trinity and would like to say what a wonderful, special lady she is. The reading was so accurate, it made me laugh (because I was being told off!!), smile and cry. It is so uplifting to know people close to my heart are still with me, and it is an absolute pleasure to know that I can trust Trinity to be my contact. Thank you so much Trinity Take care, God bless xx
fields.title: An absolute pleasure

fields.body: Tonight at The Aldridge Community Centre Trinity exceeded herself. There were few dry eyes as she gave accurate spiritual messages to each person. She was incredible and I am sure she convinced even the sceptics that were there this evening that life did exist after death. Well done Trinity hope you will soon come again and look forward to that.
fields.title: Well done Trinity

fields.body: I would like to say a big thank you to Trinity for coming out to Ludlow to give my friends and I a group reading, and what a lovely evening we had .Trinity was absolutely amazing! I must say a couple of friends had never had a reading before and not sure what to expect, but was told after that as soon as Trinity entered the room they immediately felt at ease, and that’s what happens when you first meet her, she is such a kind, caring, compassionate lady you can’t help but immediately warm towards her. The messages that came through have really helped ,comforted, and reassured my friends .This is the third time I have seen Trinity working ,and would certainly recommend her I know you will not be disappointed! I know why she was chosen to pass messages on, she is one amazing lady! Love and light Trinity. Trish and friends xx
fields.title: A big thanks

fields.body: Thank you so much for the clear, understanding and thoughtful meeting we shared last evening Trinity. The words that you passed onto me from my dad were wonderful and gave me a lot of comfort to know he is happy and well and still watching over me and my family. I was unsure before I met you as to how it could be true but came along and was shocked and delighted by how accurate and detailed you were in your messages to me  many thanks and hopefully I will meet with you in the future , best wishes,
fields.title: Wonderful words

fields.body: I've seen Trinity 3 times now and I've been comforted and amazed by her meaningful messages. I recommend Trinity to anyone who’s seeking spiritual help and I assure they will be enlightened by her genuine power.
fields.title: Enlightened by her genuine power

fields.body: I and my friend went to see Trinity in Shrewsbury last month and a murder victim came through with a message for his family that I was able to deliver. The facts of how he died were verified at the meeting as well as after when I checked with his family. Very accurate and it gave his family some comfort, so thanks Trinity. Mandy
fields.title: Very accurate

fields.body: I went along to one of Trinity’s evening’s at the assembly rooms in Ludlow. I was amazed that so many people had such great readings and the information given was very personal and significant to them. Can't wait to see you again!
fields.title: Can't wait to see you again!

fields.body: Some mediums just have a natural talent, and in Ludlow at her last show Trinity really proved that. The messages she gave were both accurate and informative, I have seen all her shows here, and felt by far this was the best supported, which only goes to prove that people will support someone who is genuine, and reaches the other side.
fields.title: A natural talent

fields.body: Meeting Trinity for a private reading some days ago has left me full of comfort and happiness knowing my mom is still so close to me, everything she said was spot on. She’s an amazing lady and I would highly recommend her to anyone. Thanks Trinity x
fields.title: Everything she said was spot on

fields.body: I had a private reading with Trinity this week, and I have to say it amazed me, she is a lovely lady and has a genuine gift! She was very accurate in everything she said, even saying names and events that had happened. I am still buzzing now from the experience, thanks a lot Trinity I hope to see you again in the future. xxxx
fields.title: It amazed me

fields.body: I live in South Africa and came across Trinity totally by chance on the internet. I wasn't seeking to contact anybody in the spirit world, but somehow it seemed preordained and a few weeks later Trinity did a reading for me via the telephone. She’s wonderful – warm, friendly and sincere – and there could be no doubt that she’s genuine. The reading itself was uncannily accurate with various messages from my late mother. All in all an amazing and spiritually satisfying experience. So don’t think that readings can only be done face to face – Trinity can bridge thousands of miles and has a very special gift.
fields.title: Trinity can bridge thousands of miles

fields.body: Thank you so much for my reading, everything you told me was spot on. I will be seeing you again soon.
fields.title: You are an amazing lady

fields.body: I saw Trinity a few weeks ago in Wolverhampton. I gained great comfort from the messages she gave me from my mother. They have given me the strength to try and live my life to the full. You have a great gift Trinity please continue to bring comfort to others in the future.
fields.title: A great gift

fields.body: I would personally like to ‘thank her’ for last night at The Cathedral Lodge Hotel-Lichfield. The evidence for me personally was incredible and spot on -she could not have known anything about me, yet she was so accurate in her messages to me. Please do not hesitate to go and see her. Thank you again Trinity and look forward to seeing you again very soon. God Bless xxx
fields.title: I would recommend to anyone

fields.body: I saw Trinity On Friday at the Cathedral Lodge Hotel in Lichfield. What an amazing evening, she was so right about everything and at the end of the evening all my dearest family that had passed over came to speak to me through Trinity, she is such a lovely lady I will go and see her again. Marguerite XX
fields.title: What an amazing evening

fields.body: Do you know wot you never cease to amaze me. Brilliant night last night true and honest they love working with you Trinity your candle will never go out I love to see people’s faces when spirit come to them keep it up girl god bless ya
fields.title: Never cease to amaze me

fields.body: I visited Trinity for the third time in two years. Once again she has convinced me (and others) about the continuation of our loved ones in spirit. Trinity is a very loving person who exudes sincerity and care. She genuinely loves her mediumship and the peace that it brings to others. As before, I highly recommend her to anyone who wants a genuine reading from the spirit world.
fields.title: Highly recommended to anyone

fields.body: Hi met Trinity for the first time last night, both me and my friend were stunned by what we were told and will be going again when she visits again thanks Trinity for everything Tania xx
fields.title: We were stunned, thanks

fields.body: My husband, daughter and myself went to a private reading with Trinity about six weeks ago and can honestly say we were amazed how accurate the information we received from our families in the spirit world. The warmth and love that came across to us from our loved ones was all we needed to comfort us on what has been quite a trying time. Thank you again Trinity for a wonderful experience.
fields.title: Thank you
